      "type": "multiple-choice",
      "text": "Berlin ist größer ___ München.",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "als"
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "wie"
        },
        {
          "id": "c",
          "text": "dass"
        },
        {
          "id": "d",
          "text": "von"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswerId": "a",
      "explanation": "Comparative + als",
      "explanationDetail": "With comparatives, use 'als' (than). Berlin ist größer als München (Berlin is bigger than Munich). Pattern: adjective + -er + als. Groß → größer.",
      "tags": [
        "comparatives",
        "adjectives",
        "als"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "q2",
      "type": "multiple-choice",
